Package: gpr
Title: Power Analysis for R
Version: 0.1.0
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Authors@R: 
    person("Steve", "Jean-Baptiste", , "sj1021433@wcupa.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive power analysis package for R implementing 
    statistical power analyses similar to those available in G*Power 3.1 
    (Faul et al., 2007). Supports t-tests, F-tests, chi-square tests, 
    z-tests, and exact tests with programmatic API, interactive console 
    menu, Shiny GUI, and publication-quality plots.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    scales,
    shiny
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    rstudioapi,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
